{
  "texts": [
    "After a while, the online document became too chaotic with the comments far exceeding the actual text in volume.",
    "At this point, we formed subgroups for each cluster.",
    "In particular, HRL suggested subgroup compositions and lead authors for each subgroup; this was based on expressed interest (in the aforementioned table or otherwise) and/or participation in the preceding discussions and work on the online document.",
    "Depending on their interests, participants were allowed to sign in and out of as many subgroups as they liked at any time and also scale their involvement (from actively writing text to reading and commenting on existing text).",
    "Either or both of the two first authors (DL and HRL) participated in (almost) each of the groups most of the time and thereby assured communication across subgroups."
  ]
}